# Project conventions (index)

Quick checklist; full wording is in the files under `.cursor/rules/`.

- **Build / dev server / typecheck**: Never run unless the user asks — `00-global-safety.mdc`.
- **Tests**: Do not add, modify, or run tests unless the user asks — `05-workflow-execution.mdc`. Vitest + Nuxt project layout and config files — `testing-vitest-nuxt.mdc`.
- **Prisma / migrations**: Shared client and migration policy — `backend-best-practices.mdc` (sections **Data Access** and **Prisma schema and migrations**). **Account membership** (`UserAccount` capabilities, list filtering) — **Data Access** in `backend-best-practices.mdc`; microservice env — `backend-security-and-ops.mdc`.
- **Code style / TS / Zod**: `10-code-style-and-ts.mdc`.
